Is it worth the efforts you made ? I am not so sure. It all depends on the way you play ! <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>1/ PET HIMSELF :</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
It is true that Epic pet is really a monster, quadding 83, proc 130 (or 140 ? well, not important) DS 50. Much better than ANY pet (well... right now, duno for new pets). 4K health. Big tank, big help.<br>
2 days ago I was in a full 60 group in UP. Tank was a warlord, with TOV armor but weapons were not really great. He said he was not sure he could duel the pet (being unbuffed of course)<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>2/ using the pet :</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> This means you will really ROCK in solo and group</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->. Epic is really a big big upgrade to any of your pet.<br>
<br>
If you <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> raid a lot</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->, epic pet is not so usefull, it is just another high level meleer.<br>
<br>
If you don't have an epic and want to rock, look at the topics here, being well trained in IR is also really BIG WAY. (but much more difficult, you must need to be really <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> good</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->... and have a lot of AA that I don't have !)<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>the quest</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
is it really so difficult ? there is a topic here who says NO, it is not really uber, it is LONG. Lots of the stuff can be soloed without any problem, even at 55.<br>
Others mob can be killed by a good group, but problem is the spawning time, and the fact that mob has not got the right stuff.<br>
Personaly, I started Epic at 55 when my guild gave me the Hate staff. <br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> I needed around 30 hours of work to get the whole solo parts</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
I camped quillmane for 30 or 40 hours, then a guildy gave cloak to me (mqed).<br>
<br>
I killed phiny and ne'ashir 3 or 4 times, then I baught both staves (3 and 4K).<br>
Guild made a big raid in plane and we got 5 crowns. 20 hours of work I think, but fun.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>4/ another example</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
A guildy is working on it. She's going to buy the whole part she can't solo, and that'll be done. <br>
..<br>
don't ask me is this is the RIGHT way of playing, this is a game, you play the way you want.<br>
may be it is her only way of getting the Epic, because it is very difficult to get a group to go to COM or KK : if we were <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> sure</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> to get the staves, ok, but you go, spend 1 hour or more, no XP, no fun, and may be no staff. boring. worst for Hate.<br>
